          MaxPoint is seeking a technical leader to guide our data scientists working on highly visible projects that improve performance and grow our product suite. You're excited by the prospect of leading and helping our team grow to solve ever more complex business problems in imaginative and innovative ways.
          Data Scientists at MaxPoint are deeply involved in all stages of product development. You'll work with our technical specialists to scope opportunities for our technology, research new methods, prototype creative new algorithms, and deploy analytic software solutions. We face challenges of solving prediction and classification problems on multiple petabytes of high-dimensional data where our customers require near real-time results.
          Your leadership will push our technology further and keep us at the forefront of our industry.
